{"title":"The History of MTB Evolution Show is This Weekend at Santa Cruz Bicycles","link":"https://theradavist.com/the-history-of-mtb-evolution-show-santa-cruz-bicycles/","date":1712931391000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/HistoryofMTB_SantaCruz.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/HistoryofMTB_SantaCruz.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/HistoryofMTB_SantaCruz.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/HistoryofMTB_SantaCruz.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/HistoryofMTB_SantaCruz.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>This weekend, April 13th and 14th, <a href=\"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/en-US\" target=\"_blank\">Santa Cruz Bicycles</a> is hosting the next <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/velo-cosmos-event/\" target=\"_blank\">Velo Cosmos</a> showcase with <a href=\"https://teamoldsoil.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Team Old Soil</a> on the history of mountain bike evolution. John will be there, documenting the fun so if you’re in the area, be sure to swing by!</p>\n<p>Santa Cruz Bicycles Factory Store<br />\n2841 Mission St Extension<br />\nSanta Cruz, CA, 95060<br />\n9 AM – 4 PM</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-history-of-mtb-evolution-show-santa-cruz-bicycles/\">The History of MTB Evolution Show is This Weekend at Santa Cruz Bicycles</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"409af5a614a180be7e6c5f00192301e964867b2ec7afc986694ac99f951439b4","category":"Cycling"}